'''Kurihara Shrine''' (栗原神社) is a [[Shinto shrine]] located in [[Takayama City]], [[Gifu Prefecture]], within the Kamitakara area (formerly [[Yoshiki District]], [[Kamitakara Village]]). It is situated near the Kamitakara Branch Office of Takayama City (formerly the Kamitakara Village Office).
The shrine is identified as one of the {{ill|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|12=draft}} listed in the {{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|12=draft}} for [[Hida Province]], being one of eight such shrines in the region.
